  "story": {
    "title": "The Prince and the Village of Peace",
    "body": "In a peaceful village, people lived with harmony and helped each other. A young prince visited the village to understand their way of life. The villagers believed that every individual should contribute to the community. One day, a sudden problem occurred when a strong force damaged part of the village. People felt upset, but they stayed calm. The prince announced help from the kingdom and allowed experts to fix the condition. Everyone worked together, dividing tasks and following instructions carefully. A wise old man explained the cause of the problem and suggested solutions. The prince listened and protected the villagers from further harm. Even though the challenge was big, they did not lose hope. The situation improved, and peace returned. The prince learned that helping others and making the right choice creates a strong community. Therefore, he promised to support the village forever.",
    "comprehension": [
      {
        "q": "Who visited the village?",
        "opts": ["king", "prince", "soldier", "farmer"],
        "ans": 1
      },
      {
