    "title": "Village Problem Discussion",
    "script": "A: Did you hear the announcement?\nB: Yes, there is a problem in the village.\nA: What is the condition?\nB: It is bad near the river.\nA: Who will help?\nB: Experts will come.\nA: That is good.\nB: The prince is also coming.\nA: We should contribute.\nB: Yes, everyone should help.\nA: Do you know the cause?\nB: Not yet.\nA: We must protect people.\nB: Yes, safety is important.\nA: Let’s follow instructions.\nB: Okay.",
